{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they said the plot wasn't successful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And later on I heard that was the plot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when Rommel and a few generals wanted to get rid of Hitler, that's the only news you heard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the work, you didn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I worked in this-- in this [NON-ENGLISH] section of the German expedition of mine where I only saw breathing holes coming up from the ground.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we knew-- and, and trucks-- motorized-- electrically motorized trucks so you couldn't even hear were going down and up in paved roads.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's where we knew that something is underground, because we all see workers, German workers, in this electricalized buggies carrying certain stuff somewhere.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't see the entrance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't see how they come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "All we saw, up from the earth, breathing holes like you have now here, the plumbers give you breathing holes when they build a building for the smell or whatever to go out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "All the other things was outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The railroad we built was we had to-- after we worked in the stone quarry, they break the stone in certain size.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then when, when we didn't have-- day was bad, we couldn't work on the stone mine, they took us out to the railway line.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they had a hammer, which looked like the hammershark's head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And with that, we had to hit the stone underneath the, the logs which carries the railway line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know how they call this little piece of very heavy thing, but it's-- and to make it level, you have to put hammer stones underneath.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So when the train comes, it's on a solid ground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It doesn't sink, and it is level.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's all I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
